HEADWORD: 1000
<hw>1000</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>denoting a quantity
consisting of one more than nine hundred ninety nine and one less than
one thousand and one; -- representing the number one thousand as Arabic
numerals</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> thousand, a thousand, one thousand, m, k</syn>⟦br⟧
